
## List of hospitals in Rwanda

This is a list of all hospitals in Rwanda. The list is not exhaustive. You can add referenced content to the list.

# Kigali City 

University Teaching Hospital of Kigali (CHUK)
Kacyiru Police Hospital
Muhima Hospital
Kibagabaga Hospital
Kanombe Military Hospital (also Rwanda Military Hospital)
King Faisal Hospital Kigali
Ndera Hospital
Masaka Hospital

# Eastern Region 

